@Node CARGOBAY "STCCG.guide/Cards/Sites/Cargo Bay"
@font diamond.font 12
@TOC SITE

@{"Main" link "XXPATH:stccg.guide/CONTENT"} @{"Universe" link "XXPATH:stccg.guide/UNIVERSE"} @{"Sites" link SITE}


    @{b}@{u}Cargo Bay@{ub}@{uu}

    @{"Site" link SITE}        Common   @{"Rules of Acquisition" link "XXPATH:roa.guide/MAIN"}

    Universal / @{"Rules of Acquisition" link "XXPATH:roa.guide/MAIN"} icon

    @{b}Smuggling, Acquisition and {Non-Aligned} Navigation personnel may report here
    (or download here in place of a normal card play; player draws no cards
    that turn). Once each turn, if a freighter, transport or {Ferengi} ship's crew
    member completes a "cargo run" (brings a non-weapon Equipment
    card here from another facility), for each mission passed (except
    starting and ending locations) owner may draw a card or download a
    Gold-Pressed Latinum here. (Once per game per Equipment card title.)
@{ub}
XXPICTURELINE

    Picture taken from the Deep Space 9 episode @{"Profit and Loss" link "XXPATH:ds9episodes.guide/DS938"}.

    For a description of terms used see @{"Legend" link LEGEND}.

