@Node DOCKINGPADS "STCCG.guide/Cards/Sites/Docking Pads"
@font diamond.font 12
@TOC SITE

@{"Main" link "XXPATH:stccg.guide/CONTENT"} @{"Universe" link "XXPATH:stccg.guide/UNIVERSE"} @{"Sites" link SITE}


    @{b}@{u}Docking Pads@{ub}@{uu}

    @{"Site" link SITE}        Uncommon   @{"Deep Space 9" link "XXPATH:ds9.guide/MAIN"}

    @{"Deep Space 9" link "XXPATH:ds9.guide/MAIN"} icon

    @{b}Any ship with no staffing requirements may report, dock (land)
    and undock (take off) here if ship is compatible with station's
    affiliation OR crew includes a V.I.P. OR player controlling ship
    has a Computer Skill personnel present at this site unopposed
    (just before undocking, that personnel may board ship). Player
    controlling station may, oncer per game, download Establish
    Landing Protocols. Capacity: 6 ships. Tractor Beam.
@{ub}
XXPICTURELINE

    For a description of terms used see @{"Legend" link LEGEND}.

@{"Main" link "XXPATH:stccg.guide/CONTENT"} @{"Universe" link "XXPATH:stccg.guide/UNIVERSE"} @{"Sites" link SITE}

