    @{"Deep Space 9" link "XXPATH:ds9.guide/MAIN"} icon

    @{b}Compatible OFFICER-classification personnel may report here.
    Any player may, in place of their normal card play, download to
    an unopposed site on this location one card which may play there
    (if reporting a ship or personnel, must be of matching affiliation);
    player draws no cards that turn. Any Computer Skill personnel
    unopposed here may commandeer station.
@{ub}
